    >

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium second_font">
      Nigeria Association of Computing Students (NACOS)
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-3">
      The Nigerian Association of Computing Students (NACOS) is a prominent
      student organization that represents students studying various IT-related
      courses in tertiary institutions across Nigeria. With over 350,000 members
      and 250 local chapters, NACOS is the largest and most organized student
      body in Africa. The association has been in existence for over two decades
      and has a presence in almost all tertiary institutions in Nigeria,
      including privately owned ones.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

